======================================================================
                     Upstream / third-party notice
======================================================================

DECUHR.jl is a Julia port and modification of the Fortran 77 DECUHR
routines published by T. O. Espelid and A. Genz, "DECUHR: An Algorithm
for Automatic Integration of Singular Functions over a Hyperrectangular
Region", Numerical Algorithms 8 (1994), 201–220.

The upstream Fortran distribution carries its own copyright notice,
reproduced verbatim in the file `NOTICE` at the root of this
repository. That notice requires that it be included in all copies of
any software which is or includes a copy or modification of the
upstream software, and in all copies of the supporting documentation
for such software.

Accordingly, every copy and every derivative work of DECUHR.jl MUST
retain both this `LICENSE` file and the accompanying `NOTICE` file
unmodified.
